<figureCitation box="[1244,1376,591,615]" captionStart="Figures 56–66" captionStartId="22.[143,233,1883,1902]" captionTargetBox="[314,1260,1661,1851]" captionTargetId="figure-217@22.[312,789,1658,1829]" captionTargetPageId="22" captionText="Figures 56–66. Melaloncha spp., ovipositors. Figs 56–60: dorsal. Figs 61–66: left lateral." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5439631" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5439631/files/figure.png" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">FIGS 59, 65</figureCitation>
